    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "Qz6jZF4zhoxLlwv38BxXVYHk31sBH6bA1hifTi5XINA=",
    "originContent": "-   **Direct Music Injection**: Add songs to your Apple Music library without a PC.",
    "translatedContent": "-   **直接音楽注入**：PCなしでApple Musicライブラリに曲を追加。"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "r3iRkge+zBWmzgoJlE7x1dZaxYe5KcCFga1oY9WX4Lk=",
    "originContent": "-   (DISABLED FOR NOW) **Ringtone Manager**: Inject custom ringtones (`.m4r` and `.mp3` auto-conversion).",
    "translatedContent": "-   （現在無効）**着信音マネージャ**：カスタム着信音（`.m4r`および`.mp3`自動変換）を注入。"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "AJr5MCm/Bllg8l1273FV24RWxK4mnWDZOobbgEmRDMU=",
    "originContent": "-   **Playlist Support**: Create and manage playlists on the fly.",
    "translatedContent": "-   **プレイリスト対応**：即座にプレイリストを作成・管理。"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "+NwY/TAaiqod9fa5btAHU9KLG1xfPV36ezksW0GSQx8=",
    "originContent": "-   **No Computer Needed** (after setup): Once paired, you're free!",
    "translatedContent": "-   **PC不要**（セットアップ後）：ペアリング後は自由！"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "xiW20mDNLfp0N3xSakFY8Q930vO1AcNga2M/zLRj3DE=",
    "originContent": "-   **Metadata Editing**: Auto-fetched from iTunes or Deezer.",
    "translatedContent": "-   **メタデータ編集**：iTunesやDeezerから自動取得。"
  },
